cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IT

The paper deals with image registration, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV). The approach presented involves learning a low-dimensional stochastic parametrization of the deformation, which is a machine learning technique (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of a conditional variational autoencoder (CVAE) is also a machine learning technique (cs.NE). Finally, the paper introduces a new differentiable exponentiation layer, which is a mathematical technique that could fall under information theory (cs.IT).
